| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1872 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 30e8d2ac-98a9-59fb-9ece-35ab79cf5910"
